    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The 13-factor assessment is complete per ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements for the stated model risk level. The package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; no context of use object is bound to this unit of assurance.",
